c creators and their works.                    article                        span                        h4                        p A massive shift in the music industry towards openness and simplification.                    article                        span                        h4                        p                            | A new form of distribution in the music industry via instant, direct sales to the listener.                    article                        span                        h4                        p                            | An easy way for an entrepreneur to collaborate with the musician, skipping out middlemen.                    article                        span                        h4                        p More inspiration for brand new music masterpieces!        .screen-status.lazy(data-src="/assets/images/cases/music-copyright/status-screen.jpg")            .container                article                    h5 STATUS                    h3 The application was successfully approved at the Proof-of-Concept stage    include ../../includes/banner    include ../../includes/newsletteralt    include ../../includes/footer    include ../../includes/popupform